---
title: HotelOps Architecture
---
flowchart TD
    WA["📱 WhatsApp"] -->|message| AGENT["🤖 @HotelOps Agent"]
    AGENT -->|log| EVENTS["Events"]
    AGENT -->|propose| YOU["👤 Stefano"]
    YOU -->|confirm| AGENT

    EVENTS -->|evaluate| ENTITIES["Entities"]
    ENTITIES -->|promoted| OBSIDIAN["📓 Obsidian"]
    ENTITIES -->|dimension update| DRIVE["📊 Google Drive"]

    subgraph SQLite ["hotelops.db"]
        EVENTS
        ENTITIES
    end

    subgraph Truth ["Source of Truth"]
        OBSIDIAN
    end

    subgraph Warehouse ["Data Warehouse"]
        DRIVE
    end

    Truth ===|authority| SQLite
    SQLite ===|authority| Warehouse

    classDef truth fill:#4a9eff,stroke:#2d7cd4,color:#fff
    classDef ops fill:#f59e0b,stroke:#d97706,color:#fff
    classDef warehouse fill:#10b981,stroke:#059669,color:#fff
    classDef agent fill:#8b5cf6,stroke:#7c3aed,color:#fff
    classDef input fill:#ef4444,stroke:#dc2626,color:#fff

    class OBSIDIAN truth
    class EVENTS,ENTITIES ops
    class DRIVE warehouse
    class AGENT agent
    class WA,YOU input
